#: ../../reference/expressions.rst:328
msgid "List displays"
msgstr "Sintaxes de criaĂ§ĂŁo de lista"

#: ../../reference/expressions.rst:338
msgid ""
"A list display is a possibly empty series of expressions enclosed in square "
"brackets:"
msgstr ""
"Uma sintaxe de criaĂ§ĂŁo de lista Ă© uma sĂ©rie possivelmente vazia de "
"expressĂ”es entre colchetes:"

#: ../../reference/expressions.rst:344
msgid ""
"A list display yields a new list object, the contents being specified by "
