"operaĂ§ĂŁo pode ser substituĂ­da pelo mĂ©todo especial :meth:`~object.__pos__`."

#: ../../reference/expressions.rst:1425
msgid ""
"The unary ``~`` (invert) operator yields the bitwise inversion of its "
